api_list.name: /topics child node count
api_list.description: Retrieves a total count of all child topic nodes.

required_parameters.name: api_key
required_parameters.description: api key

required_parameters.name: id
required_parameters.description: An integer parameter that specifies the ID of the partent topic node for which child nodes are returned. (FromUri)

required_parameters.name: getChildren
required_parameters.description: A boolean parameter that specifies to return child nodes. When [true], child nodes are returned. When [false], the parent specified parent node is returned. (FromUri)

required_parameters.name: getCount
required_parameters.description: A boolean parameter that indicates to return a count. Specifying a false value will return zero. (FromUri)
